      "para_id": "Q000923.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninḫursaĝa , the beloved mother of Ninĝirsu , the lady who had become one with the city , the mother of all children , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , built her temple in Ĝirsu ."
    }
